<A>__{he walks up the steps holding patrick, who hugs and kisses him.}
<C>__{roderick }
<D>__{my son, little patrick cosgrove, was a prince; his breeding and manners, even at his early age, showed him to be worthy of the two noble families from whom he was descended, and i don't know what high hopes i had for the boy, and indulged in a thousand fond anticipations as to his future success and figure in the world, but stern fate had determined that i should leave none of my race behind me.}
